text AquaHideout_B1F_Text_Grunt2Intro {
	"If you want to know the secret about
	our HIDEOUT, you have me to beat!"
}

text AquaHideout_B1F_Text_Grunt2Defeat {
	"I can't win at all…"
}

text AquaHideout_B1F_Text_Grunt2PostBattle {
	"Our HIDEOUT's secret?

	Well, let's just say…
	There's a submarine at the far end!

	But, by now…
	Kekekeke…"
}

text AquaHideout_B1F_Text_Grunt3Intro {
	"Fuel supply loaded A-OK!
	In-cruise snacks loaded A-OK!

	Nothing left to do but KO a pesky
	meddler!"
}

text AquaHideout_B1F_Text_Grunt3Defeat {
	"I took a serious licking!"
}

text AquaHideout_B1F_Text_Grunt3PostBattle {
	"Humph!
	This was supposed to happen!

	My mission was to just hold you up!"
}

text AquaHideout_B1F_Text_Grunt5Intro {
	"Yawn… Keeping watch over the
	HIDEOUT bores me. I'll take you on."
}

text AquaHideout_B1F_Text_Grunt5Defeat {
	"Yawn…
	Oh, I lost…"
}

text AquaHideout_B1F_Text_Grunt5PostBattle {
	"If you scurry too much, other TEAM
	AQUA members might get you."
}

text AquaHideout_B1F_Text_Grunt7Intro {
	"Hey!
	You there!

	Which do you think is cooler?
	TEAM AQUA's uniform or TEAM MAGMA's?"
}

text AquaHideout_B1F_Text_Grunt7Defeat {
	"I lost in a cool way…"
}

text AquaHideout_B1F_Text_Grunt7PostBattle {
	"If you have a cool uniform, you look
	good even in a loss, don't you think?"
}
